ren":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"0","text":"Daño Inducido por\\NVentilador (VILI)","guid":"FRFuBU80Yh1WZHmy4xqDAw","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"Programación del ventilador → importancia capital en recuperación","guid":"ZUISiOS5Zd2SlZyu4lVrpA","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"Puede causar → sepsis, SDRA, falla ventilatoria central","guid":"6ezYnMkrqm5vJyF0LAwjTw","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"128","text":"Mecanismos\\Nde daño","guid":"FxtLAMc8rmmKWPJJJGf7xA","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"**Barotrauma** → presiones meseta >30 cmH₂O","guid":"_GPm5MN5MWpKFITKfTYxgQ","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"**Volutrauma** → volúmenes corriente altos","guid":"np5jzRPUWaVVqAoojiHfQA","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"**Atelectrauma** → apertura/cierre cíclico","guid":"S6KPa5w0jramvnx0ljWugg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"**Biotrauma** → respuesta inflamatoria sistémica por VM","guid":"YYQUJzfE_Mokm3EPWjRj1A","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"128","text":"Ventiladores modernos con microprocesador → facilitan decisiones","guid":"CbmQphL7BMlRPFMRkD5AzQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"0","text":"Sedación y\\NDestete","guid":"TS_LAJvMwJkeff-dLz9wfA","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"Buenas prácticas de VM → suspensión marginal de sedación","guid":"kLDPm3Zj4EklrzB9axiO7w","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"→ ↓ duración de VM y estancia en UCI","guid":"xWNV5r8SyvqUOnTCurgjbQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"137","text":"Uso racional de relajantes neuromusculares","guid":"E90xTwu3NmI1sUmo6osa4A","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"137","text":"Aproximación integral al proceso de weaning/destete","guid":"hDcqiJ4ssupuCtjvqrzbbg","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"137","text":"Sedación en UCI","guid":"","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"Primeras guías de sedación y dolor → 2002","guid":"zjM3vf4o6FX-Ga006F_RKw","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"Dolor puede contribuir a agitación → adecuada analgesia primero","guid":"Ndx0GbqrsreWzpMsKRNk0w","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"142","text":"Opioides = base de terapia analgésica","guid":"T_Be89nb9Ky_1ubGhT4uTg","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"142","text":"Medidas no farmacológicas antes de escalar","guid":"cmvI0s5QxjTq73WX2_y8YA","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"142","text":"**Dexmedetomidina** → pilar fundamental en sedación de paciente crítico","guid":"ij6mFsxwG-g1JneoPC-9hg","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"↑ evidencia y ↓ costos → generalización de uso","guid":"7vkQJ236iDi-9bjW0KxgLg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"137","text":"Destete","guid":"","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Preparación desde soporte ventilatorio invasivo","guid":"b5BCofyqRQpV7G9g2si1aA","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"Paciente conectado al ventilador cuando condiciones en resolución","guid":"3unZruQtesGKTEf3l_ZjWw","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"Implementar medidas específicas → destete efectivo","guid":"TkGs6Opr-lPM6AwMHAIMMw","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"Aproximación integral → parámetros ventilatorios + cardiovasculares + neurológicos","guid":"XTN0EhOqN4fyKDEirjJCjw","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"149","text":"Ecocardiografía → parte integral de evaluación de destete","guid":"SPdettOe5P9dxc3dMc__8Q","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"149","text":"Falla de extubación y reintubación precoz → reconocer tempranamente","guid":"OMofrCpFeuLc0iUwpFnjxw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"0","text":"Transporte Intrahospitalario y\\NSeguridad en Imagenología","guid":"9TAruCxjLEsMQgpilvqZdg","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"Imagenología al lado de cama → objetivo potente en seguridad","guid":"bTubhkuVLV1veINkk-E7Gw","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"Transporte fuera de UCI\\N→ riesgo significativo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"**~50%** de pacientes transportados → algún grado de complicación","guid":"AAcDWqe9mTdfZRfTigUhvg","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"Agitación, hipotensión, hipertensión, hipoxemia","guid":"I9-acrVFmrIIaM0SLRhxvQ","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"Retiro de drenajes y líneas arteriales","guid":"YMNn5is2kxFIqO4q3ruNVg","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"156","text":"Estudio en trauma → transporte a radiología no modificó manejo en **76%** de casos","guid":"BIlh7r0H3r78_u3PZE_jew","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"156","text":"Ventiladores portátiles + equipo multidisciplinario → ↓ riesgo","guid":"1q2uinM1PB6fmgtl4I3CSw","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"156","text":"Radiografía de tórax\\Nportátil diaria en UCI","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"Riesgo de desplazamiento de TET, dispositivos, drenajes","guid":"TPpM7CbhfMKgguJS77Miug","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"Política restrictiva de imágenes portátiles → menores costos sin cambio en axiomas clínicos","guid":"WzESMnnOSII2vuU8_qALOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"156","text":"Limitar radiaciones ionizantes innecesarias","guid":"H7F65cqG-tFiZAABFxc74A","children":[]}]},{"id":"168","parent":"0","text":"Seguridad en Dispositivos\\NInvasivos y No Invasivos","guid":"7--4NltHd4nkoidQvnj6oA","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"Errores en uso de dispositivos → desde artefactos hasta remoción accidental","guid":"NzpVtbI2thP-jKHSO_PQlA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"Tabla 1-2: Tipos\\Nde errores","guid":"","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"Paciente-dispositivo → autoextubación","guid":"jM1k7hFxAyFZ2P3mXvwMXQ","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"Personal-dispositivo → programación incorrecta de bomba de infusión o PCA","guid":"FybuEm44pEX7uhpHgGcGkQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"Dispositivo-dispositivo → interacción entre dispositivos/módulos incorrectos","guid":"XjIHYdU7t2AeXNX2s7mEcQ","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"170","text":"Dispositivo-ambiente → desconexión, malfuncionamiento por temperaturas","guid":"NdfLN62l0ps3CQVJzVn2VA","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"168","text":"Remoción de dispositivos terapéuticos\\N→ **22.1/1,000 pacientes-día**","guid":"","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"Sonda nasogástrica **28.9%**","guid":"zvodnVtWEgodhjRX-KQT2Q","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"O₂ suplementario **23.5%**","guid":"ubOWPkgJehEw_5fYzJR3RQ","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"175","text":"Vías venosas periféricas **20.8%**","guid":"CIw5Pyqsw7Q9peCRE28JHQ","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"175","text":"Autoextubaciones → solo **48. 9%** requirió reintubación","guid":"7CC_9u2F4YcWRTN9nSAxkw","children":[]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"168","text":"**Retiro precoz y seguro de todo artefacto** → objetivo a buscar","guid":"koPVwF7JZnZM89_xvrUmqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"181","parent":"0","text":"Futilidad y Aspectos\\NFinancieros","guid":"p6O6rbAgWJOFrM9invaHuA","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"Futilidad en cuidados intensivos → tema en debate activo","guid":"Zdd62CGKHDHOep1d5N-wkQ","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"Intervenciones que prolongan vida sin efecto apreciable por paciente","guid":"CZws6LGGiuodqK8qzhfNvg","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"Según intensivistas → hasta **20%** de pacientes críticos reciben intervenciones fútiles","guid":"xpZekwnIeTurfPcuDud0Pg","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"181","text":"Balance oportunidad vs riesgo → articulado por todo el equipo","guid":"F-pfOsGfQbUwjo9ZIz286g","children":[]}]},{"id":"186","parent":"0","text":"Iniciativas para la Seguridad\\N- Conclusión","guid":"8tb71yoemxkbfr9oqL7pEg","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"Seguridad y calidad = no disociables","guid":"aal2jdVK_I1EwCXvxMgzLw","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"Mediciones de eventos específicos → caídas, úlceras por presión, retiro de sondas","guid":"mRJRQS55nyLjZ6lA7LMddA","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"Indicadores amplios (mortalidad, estancia) → no permiten corrección en tiempo real","guid":"X-H5a6gtCMBZnuWVYXjM8Q","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"186","text":"Instrumentos validados → retroalimentación continua","guid":"KL5srNZ5W3JNIHn7ZsaCGA","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"186","text":"Cambio de cultura organizacional → irreemplazable","guid":"VxSRObhmVyi5rCPXgb65oQ","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"186","text":"Tecnología de información en salud → reporte de errores → ↓ riesgo","guid":"98-rlbQJXDjam3qpoFQBJQ","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"186","text":"Calidad de atención ≠ contención de costos per se","guid":"RRtAiaqnneYUZrDjZiSeEQ","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"186","text":"**Principios bioéticos fundamentales** → guiar toda decisión para beneficiar al paciente","guid":"EC06GgTfAuqhzPq5bkIbYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas ⭐","guid":"B3Li-4ew3vnhooetS-SFiQ","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"Mortalidad UCI Chile **~23%** promedio → oportunidad de mejora en seguridad y calidad","guid":"7qaaj-RL8WK8O0cuQRmd_A","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"Cumplimiento de lavado de manos **<40%** globalmente → nada bajo 100% es aceptable","guid":"hVPzLauZbpKsi67x1sbtww","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"195","text":"Bundle ventilatorio con checklist → herramienta simple con alto impacto en ↓ NAV","guid":"BXQqlW7Z3ccvpyuDCWZs8g","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"195","text":"**Ecografía obligatoria** para instalación de CVC según AHRQ desde 2001","guid":"pwPW8Qg90N4pKTLcRw3_7w","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"195","text":"Dexmedetomidina → fármaco preferido para sedación en UCI, reemplazando benzodiazepinas","guid":"aONR3LPQoDFt529twPj-jw","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"195","text":"Transporte intrahospitalario → complicaciones en ~50% de pacientes → preferir imagenología al lado de cama","guid":"X3nrSqulh0UR6Reb9N00lg","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"195","text":"Autoextubación → solo 48.9% requiere reintubación → evaluar necesidad real de TET","guid":"2OxSDkyIFYLODYqIXrdYow","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"195","text":"Hasta 20% de intervenciones en UCI pueden ser fútiles → reflexión bioética permanente","guid":"LkGqku9hq75PL8yJImFSnQ","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"195","text":"Aspiración subglótica reemplazó profilaxis de úlceras por estrés en bundle ventilatorio actualizado","guid":"uh_AHzXF1WYl9FN8x1cA-w","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"195","text":"VILI tiene 4 mecanismos: barotrauma, volutrauma, atelectrauma, biotrauma → ventilación protectora los mitiga","guid":"8CR7k7-Q8I4jkC83xznHIQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"1. Castro R. Riesgos y oportunidades en la UCI y el paciente crítico. En: Medicina Intensiva. Parte 1: Generalidades. Cap. 1, pp. 25-33.","guid":"lJU4BmwR1_PPncg60TDFfg","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"2. Cabana MD, Rand CS, Powe NR et al. Why don't physicians follow clinical practice guidelines? JAMA. 1999;282(15):1458-65.","guid":"u-hWlnnXeGKKNqFahiWnpw","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"206","text":"3. Pronovost PJ, Holzmueller CG. Partnering for quality. J Crit Care. 2004;19(3):121-29.","guid":"Qfns1u5hiYu1ceIJLdyksg","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"206","text":"4. Reisner-Sénélar L. The birth of intensive care medicine: Björn Ibsen's records. Intensive Care Med. 2011;37:1084-86.","guid":"FIKhoO8REooZ2RB7-FFfGg","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"206","text":"5. Rossi PJ, Edmiston CE Jr. Patient safety in the critical care environment. Surg Clin North Am. 2012;92(6):1369-86.","guid":"m2fY31d6N8cb1IJEbLVHHQ","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"206","text":"6. Rupp SM, Apfelbaum JL, Blitt CD et al. Practice guidelines for central venous access. Anesthesiology. 2012;116(3):539-73.","guid":"GLJExh3ZJ4ZxDqmXuBgb9A","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"206","text":"7. James JT. A New, Evidence-based Estimate of Patient Harms Associated with Hospital Care. J Patient Saf. 2013;9(3):122-28.","guid":"IMS5cGJ7wJhMVDpAg4FyLw","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"206","text":"8. Kohn LT, Corrigan JM, Donaldson MS (IOM). To err is human: building a safer health system. Washington, DC: National Academy Press; 2000.","guid":"uaOmhzfGufELalnT_wf5Aw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":214,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"UCI/Medicina Crítica","folder":"Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica","filename":"UPC. Cap. 1 Bugedo. Riesgos y Oportunidades en la UCI y el Paciente Crítico","id":"map_2357","resolved_references":[]}